Package: MoonShineR
Title: Predicts Moonlight, Sunlight, and/or Twilight Ground Illuminance
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("C. Lok", "Poon", , "poonchiulok@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3547-1614"))
Description: predict_lux() calculates moonlight, sunlight, and/or twilight Ground Illuminance. It is intended for use in field studies where a biologist requires moonlight illuminance values as a model predictor variable.
